    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014she is a total stunner! This beauty has been pampered since day one and is in truly flawless condition. It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no stories, just a perfect ride ready for a new home. If you've been looking for that 'like-new' feel without the brand-new price tag, you've found it! Come see it for yourself; I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
