    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in true showroom condition, this vehicle is a flawless example of meticulous ownership. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster with original factory paint that has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or curb rash on the pristine alloy wheels. Inside, the cabin retains its original 'new car' scent, featuring supple, uncreased leather upholstery and high-gloss trim that remains free of any micro-scratches. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been strictly garage-kept and maintained with an open-checkbook policy at authorized service centers. This is a rare, turn-key opportunity for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered.",
