      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem! Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s spotless inside and out\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It runs like a dream and is ready for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You really have to see it in person to believe how pristine it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
